under(kValue, dValue) // Señales de entrada y salida strategy.entry(\\"Compra\\", strategy.long, when="},{"prompt":"webdriverIO как делать рефреш страницы пока не появится элемент js async","completion":"В WebDriverIO для обновления страницы, пока не появится элемент, можно использовать метод \`waitUntil()\`, который ожидает выполнение асинхронной функции, прежде чем продолжать работу. Ниже приведен пример кода, который иллюстрирует, как это можно сделать: \`\`\`javascript const { remote } = require('webdriverio'); async function refreshPageUntilElementAppears() { const browser = await remote({ // WebDriverIO настройки }); await browser.url('https://example.com'); const element = await browser.('.my-element'); await browser.waitUntil(async () => { await browser.refresh(); return await element.isExisting(); }, { timeout: 5000, // таймаут в миллисекундах timeoutMsg: 'Элемент не появился после обновления страницы', interval: 1000, // интервал между обновлениями страницы в миллисекундах }); // Выполнять действия с элементом, когда он появляется // ... await browser.deleteSession(); } refreshPageUntilElementAppears(); \`\`\` В приведенном примере WebDriverIO обновляет страницу каждую секунду, пока элемент с классом \`.my-element\` не станет видимым. Если элемент не появляется в течение 5 секунд, WebDriverIO выбрасывает ошибку с сообщением \\"Элемент не появился после обновления страницы\\". Обратите внимание, что этот код использует асинхронные функции, поэтому он должен выполняться внутри асинхронной функции или использовать функцию \`then()\` (если это допустимо в вашем контексте)."},{"prompt":"Hello","completion":"Hello! How can I assist you today?"},{"prompt":"726393*288338283828","completion":"The product of 726,393 multiplied by 288,338,283,828 is 209,654,485,616,015,704."},{"prompt":"72727282*828282828-3","completion":"The result of (72,727,282 multiplied by 828,282,828) minus 3 is 59,999,999,999,937."},{"prompt":"Ok 73737:7373737737","completion":"The ratio of 73,737 divided by 7,373,737,737 is approximately 0.009994."},{"prompt":"how create new repository on github by cmd","completion":"To create a new repository on GitHub using the command line, you need to follow these steps: 1. First, ensure that you have Git installed on your machine and the command line interface (CLI) is set up properly. 2. Open the command prompt or terminal and navigate to the directory where you want to create your repository. 3. Use the \`git init\` command to create a new Git repository in the current directory: \`\`\` git init \`\`\` 4. Next, use the following command to create a new repository on GitHub: \`\`\` git remote add origin https://github.com/USERNAME/REPO_NAME.git \`\`\` Replace \`USERNAME\` with your GitHub username and \`REPO_NAME\` with the name you want for your repository. This command connects your local repository with the remote repository on GitHub. 5. Use \`git add\` to add the files you want to include in your repository. For example, if you want to add all files in the current directory, you can use the following command: \`\`\` git add . \`\`\` 6. Commit your changes using the \`git commit\` command: \`\`\` git commit -m \\"Initial commit\\" \`\`\` Replace \\"Initial commit\\" with an appropriate commit message. 7. Finally, use the \`git push\` command to push your local repository to GitHub: \`\`\` git push -u origin master \`\`\` This command pushes your changes to the remote repository on GitHub, creating a new branch called \\"master\\". After executing these commands, your new repository should be created on GitHub."},{"prompt":"how to select the repository to push commit?","completion":"To select the repository to push your commit, you need to properly set up your Git configuration with the correct repository URL. Here's how to do it: 1. Open the command prompt or terminal. 2. Navigate to the directory of the local repository you want to push. 3. Check the remote repositories using the following command: \`\`\` git remote -v \`\`\` This command will list all the remote repositories associated with your local repository. 4. If you see the repository you want to push to in the list, skip to step 6. If not, proceed to the next step. 5. Add a new remote repository using the \`git remote add\` command. For example, if you want to add a new remote repository called \\"origin\\" with its URL, use the following command: \`\`\` git remote add origin https://github.com/USERNAME/REPO_NAME.git \`\`\` Replace \`USERNAME\` with your GitHub username and \`REPO_NAME\` with the name of the repository you want to push to. 6. If you have multiple remote repositories, you can set the repository you want to push to as the default using the \`git push\` command. For example, to push to the \\"origin\\" repository on the \\"master\\" branch: \`\`\` git push -u origin master \`\`\` This command sets the \\"origin\\" repository as the default and associates it with the \\"master\\" branch. After setting the default, you can simply run \`git push\` without additional arguments to push to this repository and branch. By following these steps, you can select the repository you want to push your commits to through the Git configuration."},{"prompt":"Alex typically falls into a specific pattern when interacting with their partner. Alex seems to be constantly worried that their partner will leave them, and constantly seeks reassurance from their partner that they are happy in the relationship. What levels of attachment-related anxiety and avoidance does Alex likely have?","completion":"Based on the given information, it is likely that Alex has high levels of attachment-related anxiety and low levels of attachment-related avoidance. Attachment-related anxiety refers to an individual's worry or fear of rejection or abandonment by their partner. Alex constantly seeking reassurance from their partner and being worried about them leaving indicates a high level of anxiety. On the other hand, attachment-related avoidance refers to an individual's discomfort with closeness and intimacy in relationships. Since Alex is constantly seeking reassurance and being worried about their partner leaving, it suggests a low level of avoidance as they are actively seeking closeness and connection with their partner. Therefore, Alex likely has high levels of attachment-related anxiety and low levels of attachment-related avoidance."},{"prompt":"Le rôle d'un administrateur dans la gestion d'inscription dans une école","completion":"L'administrateur joue un rôle essentiel dans la gestion des inscriptions dans une école. Voici quelques-unes de ses responsabilités principales : 1. Collecte et traitement des demandes d'inscription : L'administrateur est chargé de collecter les demandes d'inscription des nouveaux élèves et de les traiter en fonction des critères d'admissibilité de l'école. Il s'assure de la complétude des dossiers et de la véracité des informations fournies. 2. Communication avec les parties concernées : L'administrateur est en charge de communiquer avec les parents ou les tuteurs légaux des élèves potentiels pour répondre à leurs questions sur le processus d'inscription, les exigences de l'école et les documents requis. Il peut également organiser des réunions d'information ou des journées portes ouvertes pour présenter l'école aux familles intéressées. 3. Planification des admissions : L'administrateur collabore étroitement avec la direction de l'école pour planifier et organiser les admissions en fonction des capacités d'accueil de l'établissement. Il peut établir des listes d'attente et planifier des entretiens ou des tests pour sélectionner les élèves les plus adaptés à l'école. 4. Gestion des dossiers d'inscription : L'administrateur est responsable de la tenue à jour et de la sécurité des dossiers d'inscription des élèves, qu'il s'agisse de dossiers papier ou numériques. Il doit s'assurer du respect de la confidentialité des informations personnelles des élèves et de leur protection conformément aux lois et réglementations en vigueur. 5. Collaboration avec les autres départements : L'administrateur travaille en étroite collaboration avec d'autres départements, tels que le service financier, le service des ressources humaines et le département pédagogique, pour coordonner les différents aspects de la gestion des inscriptions. Il peut, par exemple, collaborer avec le service financier pour régler les frais de scolarité ou avec le département pédagogique pour organiser des tests d'admission. 6. Suivi post-inscription : Une fois que les élèves sont admis, l'administrateur veille à ce que toutes les procédures administratives post-inscription soient respectées. Cela peut inclure la collecte de documents supplémentaires, la coordination des uniformes scolaires, la planification des emplois du temps des élèves, etc. En résumé, l'administrateur joue un rôle clé dans la gestion des inscriptions dans une école, en s'assurant que le processus est organisé, efficace et transparent pour les familles et l'établissement scolaire."},{"prompt":"Le rôle du secrétaire dans une école","completion":"Le rôle d'un secrétaire dans une école est également très important et comporte plusieurs responsabilités spécifiques. Voici quelques-unes des tâches principales d'un secrétaire d'école : 1. Accueil des visiteurs : Le secrétaire est souvent la première personne que les visiteurs rencontrent lorsqu'ils se rendent à l'école. Il est chargé d'accueillir les parents, les élèves, le personnel et les autres personnes de manière courtoise et professionnelle. 2. Gestion des appels téléphoniques : Le secrétaire est responsable de répondre aux appels téléphoniques et de les acheminer vers les personnes concernées. Il peut également répondre aux questions générales sur l'école ou prendre des messages en l'absence du personnel visé. 3. Gestion du courrier et des e-mails : Le secrétaire triera et distribuera le courrier postal et les e-mails entrants. Il sera le point de contact principal pour la correspondance de l'école et s'assurera que les messages sont transmis aux personnes appropriées. 4. Tenue des registres et des dossiers : Le secrétaire est chargé de maintenir et de gérer les registres et les dossiers de l'école. Cela peut inclure les dossiers des élèves, les dossiers du personnel, les rapports d'inscription, les documents administratifs, etc. 5. Gestion des absences et des retards : Le secrétaire est responsable de suivre les absences et les retards des élèves. Il peut tenir un registre des absences, prendre des appels des parents pour signaler les absences et informer les enseignants des absences à prendre en compte dans les enregistrements. 6. Soutien administratif : Le secrétaire peut fournir un soutien administratif à la direction et au personnel de l'école. Cela peut inclure la planification de réunions, la gestion des emplois du temps, la préparation de documents, la gestion des fournitures de bureau, etc. 7. Préparation des documents officiels : Le secrétaire peut être chargé de préparer et de générer divers documents officiels, tels que les bulletins scolaires, les relevés de notes, les certificats, les lettres aux parents, etc. 8. Collaboration avec les autres départements : Le secrétaire travaille en étroite collaboration avec d'autres départements de l'école, tels que les finances, les ressources humaines et le département pédagogique, pour assurer une communication fluide et efficace. En résumé, le secrétaire joue un rôle clé dans la gestion administrative d'une école. Il est responsable de l'accueil, de la communication, de la tenue des registres, de la gestion des absences, du soutien administratif et de la collaboration avec les autres départements."},{"prompt":"Le rôle d'un intendant dans une école","completion":"Le rôle d'un intendant dans une école est essentiel pour assurer le bon fonctionnement des opérations quotidiennes de l'établissement. Voici quelques-unes des responsabilités principales d'un intendant : 1. Gestion des installations : L'intendant est responsable de la gestion des installations physiques de l'école, y compris les bâtiments, les terrains, les salles de classe, les laboratoires, les installations sportives, etc. Il s'assure que ces espaces sont sécurisés, propres, bien entretenus et conformes aux normes de sécurité. 2. Maintenance et réparations : L'intendant supervise la maintenance régulière des équipements et des infrastructures de l'école. Il identifie les problèmes éventuels, organise les réparations nécessaires, coordonne les prestataires de services externes si besoin, gère les contrats de maintenance et veille à ce que les travaux soient effectués de manière efficace et dans les délais. 3. Gestion des approvisionnements : L'intendant est responsable de la gestion des approvisionnements pour l'école, y compris les fournitures de bureau, les fournitures scolaires, les équipements, les uniformes scolaires, etc. Il établit les commandes, négocie avec les fournisseurs, surveille les stocks et veille à ce que les ressources nécessaires soient disponibles en temps voulu. 4. Gestion des services de restauration : Si l'école dispose d'un service de restauration, l'intendant peut être responsable de sa gestion. Cela peut inclure la planification des menus, la coordination avec les prestataires de services alimentaires, la gestion des stocks alimentaires, la supervision du personnel de restauration, la veille au respect des normes d'hygiène et de sécurité, etc. 5. Sécurité : L'intendant est chargé de veiller à la sécurité des élèves, du personnel et des biens de l'école. Il met en place des protocoles de sécurité, organise des exercices d'évacuation en cas d'urgence, gère les systèmes de sécurité tels que les alarmes incendie et les caméras de surveillance, et collabore avec les autorités compétentes pour garantir un environnement sécurisé. 6. Gestion des ressources humaines : L'intendant peut être responsable de la gestion du personnel non-enseignant de l'école, tels que les agents de nettoyage, les agents d'entretien, les jardiniers, les cuisiniers, etc. Il participe au processus de recrutement, assure la formation et l'évaluation des employés, gère les horaires de travail et les congés, et veille à ce que les réglementations du travail soient respectées. 7. Budget et finances : L'intendant peut collaborer avec le service financier de l'école pour développer et gérer le budget alloué aux opérations et à la maintenance de l'établissement. Il s'assure que les dépenses sont conformes au budget établi, recherche des opportunités d'économie, négocie avec les fournisseurs et tient des registres précis des dépenses. En résumé, l'intendant joue un rôle clé dans la gestion des installations, de la maintenance, des approvisionnements, de la sécurité, des ressources humaines et des finances de l'école. Son travail contribue à créer un environnement d'apprentissage sûr et fonctionnel pour les élèves et le personnel."},{"prompt":"Rôle de percepteur dans une école","completion":"Le rôle d'un percepteur dans une école est lié à la gestion financière et administrative de l'établissement. Voici quelques-unes des responsabilités principales d'un percepteur : 1. Gestion des finances : Le percepteur est responsable de la gestion des finances de l'école. Il s'occupe de la collecte des frais de scolarité, des paiements des parents, des factures fournisseurs, des achats, de la tenue des comptes et de la préparation des budgets financiers de l'établissement. 2. Suivi des paiements : Le percepteur veille à ce que tous les paiements des parents ou des tuteurs légaux soient effectués en temps voulu. Il gère les systèmes de paiement en ligne, effectue des suivis réguliers des arriérés de paiement et collabore avec les parents pour résoudre les problèmes de financement. 3. Facturation et déclarations : Le percepteur émet les factures de scolarité et de frais supplémentaires, tels que les frais de cantine, les frais d'activités extrascolaires, etc. Il peut également être responsable de la préparation des déclarations fiscales liées aux frais de scolarité, conformément aux réglementations en vigueur. 4. Gestion de la trésorerie : Le percepteur gère la trésorerie de l'école, en s'assurant que les fonds sont correctement déposés et sécurisés. Il peut également surveiller les comptes bancaires de l'école et effectuer des rapprochements réguliers pour assurer une gestion financière précise. 5. Rapports financiers : Le percepteur est responsable de la préparation et de la présentation de rapports financiers réguliers à la direction de l'école. Ces rapports peuvent inclure des bilans, des états des revenus et des dépenses, des prévisions budgétaires, etc. 6. Collabore avec les fournisseurs : Le percepteur travaille en étroite collaboration avec les fournisseurs de l'école pour gérer les contrats, négocier les tarifs, assurer le suivi des paiements et résoudre les éventuels problèmes financiers. 7. Respect des réglementations : Le percepteur s'assure que toutes les activités financières de l'école sont conformes aux réglementations en vigueur, y compris celles liées aux impôts, à la comptabilité et à la facturation. 8. Confidentialité et protection des données : Le percepteur est responsable de la confidentialité et de la protection des données financières des élèves et de l'école. Il doit s'assurer que toutes les informations financières sont stockées en toute sécurité et que les procédures de traitement des données sont respectées. En résumé, le percepteur joue un rôle crucial dans la gestion financière et administrative d'une école. Il gère les finances, suit les paiements, émet les factures, assure la conformité réglementaire, prépare les rapports financiers et collabore avec les fournisseurs. Son travail contribue à assurer une bonne santé financière de l'établissement et à garantir une gestion transparente et efficace des ressources financières."},{"prompt":"Le rôle d'un directeur des études dans une école","completion":"Le directeur des études occupe un rôle important dans la gestion pédagogique d'une école. Ses responsabilités principales sont liées à la planification, à l'organisation et à la supervision du programme d'enseignement et des activités éducatives de l'établissement. Voici quelques-unes de ses responsabilités principales : 1. Développement du programme d'enseignement : Le directeur des études collabore avec l'équipe pédagogique pour développer le programme d'enseignement de l'école. Il s'assure que le programme est en conformité avec les normes éducatives locales et nationales, répond aux besoins des élèves et favorise leur développement académique et personnel. 2. Planification des cours et des emplois du temps : Le directeur des études est responsable de la planification des cours et de l'élaboration des emplois du temps pour les enseignants et les élèves. Il veille à ce que les cours soient équilibrés, cohérents et adaptés aux niveaux et aux besoins des élèves. 3. Supervision des enseignants : Le directeur des études supervise le travail des enseignants de l'école. Il observe les cours, coordonne les formations pédagogiques, assure le suivi des progressions des programmes, encourage l'innovation pédagogique et fournit une rétroaction constructive aux enseignants pour améliorer leur pratique. 4. Gestion des évaluations : Le directeur des études supervise les évaluations et les examens de l'école. Il s'assure que les évaluations sont justes, valides et conformes aux normes éducatives en vigueur. Il analyse les résultats des évaluations et utilise ces données pour identifier les forces et les faiblesses de l'apprentissage des élèves et mettre en place des actions d'amélioration. 5. Suivi des élèves : Le directeur des études suit le progrès académique des élèves. Il analyse les résultats scolaires, identifie les besoins des élèves en matière de soutien pédagogique, propose des mesures d'intervention pour les élèves en difficulté et collabore avec les enseignants et les parents pour mettre en place des plans d'action adaptés. 6. Coordination des activités extrascolaires : Le directeur des études est souvent chargé de coordonner les activités extrascolaires de l'école, telles que les clubs, les sorties éducatives, les compétitions sportives, etc. Il veille à ce que ces activités complémentent le programme d'enseignement et offrent des opportunités d'apprentissage et de développement aux élèves. 7. Collaboration avec les parents : Le directeur des études travaille en étroite collaboration avec les parents des élèves. Il communique régulièrement avec eux pour partager des informations sur le progrès scolaire de leurs enfants, les activités pédagogiques, les évaluations, etc. Il encourage également la participation et la collaboration des parents dans l'éducation de leurs enfants. 8. Veille pédagogique : Le directeur des études reste à jour sur les nouvelles tendances et les meilleures pratiques pédagogiques. Il participe à des formations, lit des articles spécialisés, assiste à des conférences et établit des collaborations avec d'autres professionnels de l'éducation pour maintenir un haut niveau de qualité dans l'enseignement et l'apprentissage à l'école. En résumé, le directeur des études joue un rôle essentiel dans la gestion pédagogique d'une école. Il est responsable de la planification, de l'organisation et de la supervision du programme d'enseignement, de la coordination des enseignants, du suivi des élèves et de la liaison avec les parents. Son travail vise à assurer une éducation de qualité et à favoriser le développement académique et personnel des élèves."},{"prompt":"Le rôle d'un élève dans une école","completion":"Le rôle d'un élève dans une école est d'abord et avant tout d'apprendre et de se développer sur les plans académique, social et personnel. Voici quelques-unes des responsabilités principales d'un élève : 1. Engagement académique : L'élève doit s'engager à participer activement à son apprentissage, en écoutant attentivement en classe, en posant des questions, en réalisant des devoirs et en étudiant régulièrement. Il doit se fixer des objectifs académiques et faire de son mieux pour les atteindre. 2. Respecter les règles et les normes de l'école : L'élève est responsable de respecter les règles et les normes de conduite établies par l'école. Cela comprend le respect des enseignants, des autres élèves, du matériel scolaire et des locaux de l'école. 3. Assister régulièrement aux cours : L'élève doit assister régulièrement aux cours et arriver à"},{"prompt":"[there would be dialogue in this story - alongside a title:] (It was just another day in the world of \\"Azur Lane\\". The commander was looking over the shipgirls of the Iron Blood. Just then, one of the Iron Blood's battleship shipgirls - Bismarck - started to feel...odd. Her left eye had come replaced with a red mass with a yellow eye - and the eye's pupil looked eerily similar to an octopus' pupil. She also had 8 red tentacles jutting out of her back - thankfully, they were noticeably short for now. However, not even medical ships can find out had had happened to Bismarck.)","completion":"Title: \\"Crimson Fate\\" Commander: (Concerned) Bismarck, are you feeling alright? You look... different. Bismarck: (Slightly panicked) Commander, I don't know what's happening to me. I can't feel my left eye, and these tentacles... I'm scared. Commander: Let's not panic just yet. We'll figure this out together. Let's get you to Akashi, maybe she can shed some light on what's happening. (They make their way to Akashi's workshop, where the repair ship examines Bismarck's condition.) Akashi: Nyaa~ This is quite perplexing. I've never seen anything like this before. We may need to delve deeper into the abyssal database for answers. Commander: Abyssal? Could Bismarck have been compromised by some sort of enemy infiltration? Bismarck: (Anxiously) No, Commander, I swear it's not that. I haven't encountered any enemies recently, let alone abyssals. Akashi: It seems we are faced with a mystery, Commander. I will start the analysis, but it may take some time to uncover the truth. Weeks pass, with Bismarck's condition worsening. Her tentacles grow longer, and the eye's presence becomes more unsettling. The Iron Blood shipgirls stand by her side, offering support and helping her adapt to her newfound state. Roon: (Determined) Bismarck, we will find a way to help you. We will not let you face this alone. Tirpitz: We are the Iron Blood, and we stand united. No matter what, we will find a solution together. Bismarck: (Grateful) Thank you, everyone. Your unwavering support gives me strength. Akashi: (Excited) Commander, I think I've made a breakthrough! It appears that Bismarck's condition is not an enemy invasion, but a unique phenomenon caused by advanced technology. Commander: Advanced technology? But how did Bismarck come into contact with it? Bismarck: (Remembering) Wait, there was an abandoned research facility we explored a while back. I found some strange artifacts there. They must have triggered this transformation! Akashi: That makes sense, nya! We need to find a way to reverse the effects and restore Bismarck to her former self. (The team works tirelessly, combining their knowledge and resources to devise a plan.) Weeks turn into months, but their efforts pay off. Bismarck's transformation starts to reverse, her tentacles receding, and her eye returning to its original form. Bismarck: (Relieved) I can't believe it. I'm back to normal. Thank you all for never giving up on me. Commander: (Smiling) Bismarck, you're not just a battleship; you're family. We would fight alongside you through anything. Bismarck: (Touched) I am truly grateful for your unwavering support. From now on, I will fight even harder for the Iron Blood and for all of us. As the skies clear, Bismarck sails forward, ready to face any new challenges that come her way. With the strength of her comrades and the commander's guidance, she knows she can overcome anything fate throws at her."},{"prompt":"Give me key points for a PowerPoint presentation slide for the following essay:  The strongest skills represented within the company/team of the small business history-based streaming service start-up could include: 1. Content creation: The ability to research and curate historical content, documentaries, and series. 2. Technical expertise: Knowledge of video streaming technology, platform development, and UX/UI design. 3. Marketing and promotion: Skills in digital marketing, social media, and content promotion to attract and engage Egyptian users. 4. Customer support: Providing efficient and helpful assistance to users, ensuring a seamless streaming experience. 5. Business development: Identifying and negotiating partnerships with historical organizations, filmmakers, and content providers. In terms of skills gaps, the company/team might face challenges in: 1. Arabic language fluency: Having team members who are proficient in Arabic would be beneficial to better understand and cater to the needs of Egyptian users. 2. Legal and copyright knowledge: Ensuring compliance with copyright laws and acquiring necessary licenses for streaming historical content. 3. Financial expertise: Managing the financial aspects of the business, including budgeting, forecasting, and securing funding. The company/team is known for doing well in: 1. Content curation and quality: Providing a wide range of historical content that appeals to Egyptian users. 2. User experience: Offering an intuitive and user-friendly streaming platform, ensuring a seamless experience. 3. Customer support: Promptly addressing user queries and issues to maintain a high level of user satisfaction. To assess if the current employees/team members have the ability to do the job, the start-up could consider: 1. Reviewing their resumes and previous work experience related to content creation, technical roles, marketing, customer support, and business development. 2. Conducting interviews and assessing their knowledge, skills, and passion for historical content and streaming industry. 3. Requesting work samples or giving them test projects to evaluate their abilities and competence. Skills can be monitored and assessed through: 1. Regular performance evaluations: Managers can assess employees’ skills during performance reviews and provide feedback for improvement. 2. Metrics and analytics: Analyzing key performance indicators such as user engagement, customer satisfaction, and revenue growth can help identify areas where skills need improvement. 3. Training and development programs: Offering training sessions or workshops to enhance employees’ skills and fill any gaps identified. 4. Seeking feedback from users: Gathering feedback from Egyptian users can provide insights into the effectiveness of the team’s skills and identify areas for improvement.","completion":"5. Conducting employee surveys: Collecting feedback from team members themselves can help identify any skills gaps or areas where additional training may be needed."},{"prompt":"sposoby na podniesienie mocy w silniku 1,4 BXW","completion":"W celu zwiększenia mocy w silniku 1.4 BXW, można rozważyć kilka sposobów: 1. Chiptuning: Można zainstalować chip tuningowy, który wpływa na oprogramowanie sterujące silnikiem, co pozwala na zwiększenie mocy. 2. Wymiana układu wydechowego: Można zamontować sportowy układ wydechowy o większej średnicy, co poprawia przepływ spalin i zwiększa wydajność. 3. Wymiana filtra powietrza: Montaż wydajniejszego filtra powietrza może poprawić dopływ powietrza do silnika, zwiększając tym samym moc. 4. Instalacja kolektora ssącego: Wymiana standardowego kolektora ssącego na bardziej wydajny może zwiększyć wydajność silnika. 5. Montaż turbosprężarki: Dodanie turbosprężarki do silnika 1.4 BXW może znacznie zwiększyć jego moc poprzez podnoszenie ciśnienia ładowania. 6. Zwiększenie stopnia sprężania: Podniesienie stopnia sprężania silnika może zwiększyć moc, jednak jest to zaawansowana procedura, która wymaga dokładnej analizy i dopasowania innych podzespołów silnika. Nie zapominaj, że wszelkie modyfikacje samochodu mogą mieć wpływ na bezpieczeństwo i niektóre z nich mogą naruszać przepisy drogowe. Przed przystąpieniem do zmian w silniku, zawsze warto skonsultować się z profesjonalnym mechanikiem lub specjalistą w dziedzinie modyfikacji samochodowych."},{"prompt":"اكتب لي منشور فيسبوك عن جروب كتب PDF","completion":"مرحبًا أصدقائي المحبين للقراءة! لقد أنشأت لكم اليوم جروب رائع يهدف إلى مشاركة كتب الـPDF المدهشة والمفيدة. في هذا الجروب، ستجدون مجموعة متنوعة من الكتب الإلكترونية المجانية بصيغة PDF، التي تغطي مختلف المجالات العلمية والأدبية والثقافية. ستجدون هنا كنزًا حقيقيًا من العلم والمعرفة، حيث سنشارك معًا أحدث الإصدارات والكتب الكلاسيكية التي تعتبر مرجعًا في مجالاتها. ليس هنالك أفضل من الحصول على معرفة مجانية، صحيح؟ ستتاح لكم فرصة تجربة ثروة من المعلومات والقصص الشيقة من خلال هذه الكتب. باستخدام الروابط المُقدَمة، يمكنكم تنزيل الكتب بسهولة والاستمتاع بالقراءة في أي وقت ومن أي مكان. هذا الجروب ليس مجرد مكان لتحميل الكتب، بل هو أيضًا مجتمع ناشط حيث يمكنكم تبادل الآراء والنقاش حول الكتب التي قرأتم. هذا يعني أنكم ستتعرفون على مثلي القراء الآخرين وستتاح لكم الفرصة لتوسيع دائرة معارفكم والاستفادة من تجارب متنوعة. أصدقائي، دعونا نكون معًا في رحلة تعليمية رائعة وممتعة من خلال مشاركة الكتب الرقمية المذهلة في هذا الجروب. انضموا إلينا الآن وشاركوا معنا أفضل الكتب والإحساس بالرضا عن توسيع آفاقنا العقلية. رابط الجروب: [ضع هنا رابط الجروب إن وجد] لا تترددوا في دعوة أصدقائكم المقربين والأحباب للانضمام أيضًا، فكُلّما زاد عددنا، كُلّما زاد تنوع محتوى الكتب التي نشاركها. كُنوا صرحًا للقراءة، وساهموا في صنع مجتمع قوي متحمس للمعرفة! نراكم في الجروب. شاركوا هذا المنشور لنشر الفائدة وجعل القراءة متعة افتراضية للجميع."},{"prompt":"Возьми текст английском языке после двоеточия , подробно проверь его, в том числе на правильность предлогов, и исправь в нем ошибки, и верни исправленный текст также в английском языке, после исправленного текста напиши на русском языке 1 список основных исправлений, которые ты сделал, и в чем именно заключалась ошибка, а также покажи что ты исправил (также на английском языке) и на что заменил ( также на английском языке), в этом списке исправлений укажи на русском языке почему ты решил исправить именно так, можешь даже сослаться на какое то правило, если ошибка была в написании какого то слова, обязательно укажи какой вариант был неправильный и на что ты исправил, также, если ты вставил какой то предлог или поменял его, обязательно считай это за ошибку и указывай это что и где ты добавил, а также почему, если ты ничего не исправлял, то ссылаться на это не нужно, а также исправления переводить с русского на английский не нужно. : My family is very big! I live with my mother, father, and my two brother. My oldest brother is 20 years old, and the other one is 10. I also have one sister, she is 15 year old. We all live in a small house near to the school. My mother work as a nurse, and my father is a teacher. We have a dog, it name is Max, and he is 3 year old. I love my family very much!","completion":"My family is very big! I live with my mother, father, and my two brothers. My oldest brother is 20 years old, and the other one is 10. I also have one sister, she is 15 years old. We all live in a small house near the school. My mother works as a nurse, and my father is a teacher. We have a dog, its name is Max, and he is 3 years old. I love my family very much! Список исправлений: 1. Исправлено \\"brother\\" на \\"brothers\\" - ошибка во множественном числе. 2. Исправлено \\"year old\\" на \\"years old\\" - ошибка во множественном числе. 3. Исправлено \\"it\\" на \\"its\\" - ошибка в указательном местоимении для животного. 4. Исправлено \\"year old\\" на \\"years old\\" - ошибка во множественном числе. Ошибки исправлены для соответствия грамматическим правилам английского языка."},{"prompt":"Give me key points for a PowerPoint presentation slide for the following essay: • Skills – POINT 8  The strongest skills represented within the company/team of the small business history-based streaming service start-up could include: 1. Content creation: The ability to research and curate historical content, documentaries, and series. 2. Technical expertise: Knowledge of video streaming technology, platform development, and UX/UI design. 3. Marketing and promotion: Skills in digital marketing, social media, and content promotion to attract and engage Egyptian users. 4. Customer support: Providing efficient and helpful assistance to users, ensuring a seamless streaming experience. 5. Business development: Identifying and negotiating partnerships with historical organizations, filmmakers, and content providers. In terms of skills gaps, the company/team might face challenges in: 1. Arabic language fluency: Having team members who are proficient in Arabic would be beneficial to better understand and cater to the needs of Egyptian users. 2. Legal and copyright knowledge: Ensuring compliance with copyright laws and acquiring necessary licenses for streaming historical content. 3. Financial expertise: Managing the financial aspects of the business, including budgeting, forecasting, and securing funding. The company/team is known for doing well in: 1. Content curation and quality: Providing a wide range of historical content that appeals to Egyptian users. 2. User experience: Offering an intuitive and user-friendly streaming platform, ensuring a seamless experience. 3. Customer support: Promptly addressing user queries and issues to maintain a high level of user satisfaction. To assess if the current employees/team members have the ability to do the job, the start-up could consider: 1. Reviewing their resumes and previous work experience related to content creation, technical roles, marketing, customer support, and business development. 2. Conducting interviews and assessing their knowledge, skills, and passion for historical content and streaming industry. 3. Requesting work samples or giving them test projects to evaluate their abilities and competence. Skills can be monitored and assessed through: 1. Regular performance evaluations: Managers can assess employees’ skills during performance reviews and provide feedback for improvement. 2. Metrics and analytics: Analyzing key performance indicators such as user engagement, customer satisfaction, and revenue growth can help identify areas where skills need improvement. 3. Training and development programs: Offering training sessions or workshops to enhance employees’ skills and fill any gaps identified. 4. Seeking feedback from users: Gathering feedback from Egyptian users can provide insights into the effectiveness of the team’s skills and identify areas for improvement.","completion":"5. Collaboration and teamwork: Assessing how well team members work together and support each other in achieving goals and delivering high-quality content and services."},{"prompt":"why do we use unlimited recognition in zuora","completion":"In Zuora, unlimited recognition is used to handle revenue recognition for subscription-based businesses. Here are a few reasons why unlimited recognition is used: 1. Subscription-based revenue recognition: In subscription businesses, revenue is recognized over the life of the subscription rather than upfront. Unlimited recognition allows businesses to recognize revenue continuously as customers continue to utilize the service or consume the product. 2. Complex revenue recognition scenarios: Some subscription businesses have complex revenue recognition scenarios like multi-element arrangements, bundling of products/services, or different pricing tiers. Unlimited recognition provides the flexibility to handle these scenarios and ensures accurate recognition of revenue. 3. Compliance with accounting standards: Unlimited recognition helps businesses stay compliant with accounting standards such as ASC 606 or IFRS 15. These standards require revenue recognition to be aligned with the transfer of goods and services to the customer, which unlimited recognition enables. 4. Accurate financial reporting: Unlimited recognition ensures that revenue is recognized in a timely and accurate manner, reflecting the actual value delivered to customers. This enables businesses to generate accurate financial statements and reports. 5. Subscription management: Apart from revenue recognition, unlimited recognition in Zuora also helps track and manage subscriptions, including billing, invoices, renewals, and cancellations. It provides businesses with a comprehensive solution for subscription management. Overall, unlimited recognition in Zuora is used to cater to the unique revenue recognition needs of subscription-based businesses and ensure accurate accounting practices while providing flexibility and ease of subscription management."},{"prompt":"If my change has unlimited recongnition as revenue rule, On my invoice postig for that charge will have revenue schedule and how","completion":"In Zuora, if your charge has the \\"Unlimited recognition\\" revenue rule, the invoice posting for that charge will still have a revenue schedule. The revenue schedule represents the timing and amount of revenue recognition for the charge. Here's how the revenue schedule works in this scenario: 1. Initial recognition: When the charge is first invoiced, the revenue schedule will create an initial recognition entry. This entry represents the recognized revenue amount for the specific period covered by the invoice. 2. Ongoing recognition: As each period progresses, the revenue schedule will automatically generate additional recognition entries based on the \\"Unlimited recognition\\" rule. These entries represent the continuous recognition of revenue over the life of the subscription. 3. Updates to the revenue schedule: If there are any changes to the subscription, such as amendments, upgrades, or downgrades, the revenue schedule will be updated accordingly. The updates will reflect the revised revenue recognition amounts for each period. 4. Consolidation of revenue: When the invoice is posted, the revenue schedule entries are consolidated to calculate the total recognized revenue for that specific invoice. This consolidated amount will be reflected in the financial statements and reports. By using the revenue schedule, Zuora provides visibility into how revenue recognition is distributed over time for each charge. It ensures accurate and compliant revenue recognition while enabling businesses to monitor their subscription revenue effectively."},{"prompt":"Hello","completion":"Hi! How can I assist you today?"},{"prompt":"5,6*8,5","completion":"The result of 5 multiplied by 8.5 is 42.5."},{"prompt":"7464773*877373737373737737373737","completion":"The result of 7,464,773 multiplied by 877,373,737,373,737,737,373,737 is a very large number: 6,547,288,475,668,989,817,731,648,161."},{"prompt":"test","completion":"Hello! How can I assist you today?"},{"prompt":"[there would be dialogue in this story - alongside a title:] (It was just another day in the world of \\"Azur Lane\\". The commander was looking over the shipgirls of the Iron Blood. Just then, one of the Iron Blood's battleship shipgirls - Bismarck - started to feel...odd. Her left eye had come replaced with a red mass with a yellow eye - and the eye's pupil looked eerily similar to an octopus' pupil. She also had 8 red tentacles jutting out of her back - thankfully, they were noticeably short for now. But not even medical ships can find out had had happened to Bismarck. However, she seems to accept the strange red mass and tentacles as part of her.)","completion":"Title: \\"Red Skies, Iron Blood\\" Commander: Bismarck, are you feeling any better today? Bismarck: *Sighs* I suppose as good as I can feel with these... additions. Commander: It's been weeks, and no one can figure out what's happening to you. Are you sure you're alright? Bismarck: I may not understand it completely, but I've come to accept this new part of me. It feels familiar somehow, like an ancient power awakening within. Commander: But Bismarck, this can't be natural. We need to find a way to revert you back to your original form. Bismarck: There's no turning back now, Commander. I can feel the energy flowing through these tentacles. They've granted me new abilities, ones that surpass my previous limitations. Commander: But at what cost, Bismarck? Your health, your identity... I can't just stand by and watch you suffer. Bismarck: Commander, I appreciate your concern, but I am not suffering. In fact, I feel stronger than ever before. The power within me is formidable, and I'm ready to prove it on the battlefield. Commander: Bismarck, I understand your desire to protect our fleet, but we can't risk losing you. We have to find a solution. Bismarck: Sometimes sacrifices must be made for the greater good, Commander. I am still the Iron Blood battleship, ready to defend our cause, no matter the form I take. Commander: *Sighs* You've always been so stubborn, Bismarck. Just promise me you'll be careful out there. Bismarck: Of course, Commander. I won't let this power consume me. Trust me, I've learned to control it. As the red skies loomed over the Iron Blood fleet, Bismarck set sail once again, her red mass and tentacles a symbol of her transformed self. With each battle, she showcased her newfound strength, earning the respect and awe of her fellow shipgirls. And though the mystery of her transformation remained unsolved, Bismarck stood tall, ready to face any challenge that came her way."},{"prompt":"viết 1 đoạn code để tính tổng và thương 2 phân số 1/2 và 3/4","completion":"Đoạn code sau tính tổng và thương của hai phân số 1/2 và 3/4: \`\`\`python # Định nghĩa class Fraction class Fraction: def __init__(self, numerator, denominator): self.numerator = numerator self.denominator = denominator def add(self, other): result_numerator = self.numerator * other.denominator + other.numerator * self.denominator result_denominator = self.denominator * other.denominator return Fraction(result_numerator, result_denominator) def divide(self, other): result_numerator = self.numerator * other.denominator result_denominator = self.denominator * other.numerator return Fraction(result_numerator, result_denominator) # Khởi tạo hai phân số fraction1 = Fraction(1, 2) fraction2 = Fraction(3, 4) # Tính tổng của hai phân số sum_fraction = fraction1.add(fraction2) print(\\"Tổng của 1/2 và 3/4 là:\\", sum_fraction.numerator, \\"/\\", sum_fraction.denominator) # Tính thương của hai phân số divide_fraction = fraction1.divide(fraction2) print(\\"Thương của 1/2 và 3/4 là:\\", divide_fraction.numerator, \\"/\\", divide_fraction.denominator) \`\`\` Kết quả được in ra sẽ là: \`\`\` Tổng của 1/2 và 3/4 là: 10 / 8 Thương của 1/2 và 3/4 là: 4 / 6 \`\`\` Chúng ta đã thực hiện thành công việc tính tổng và thương của hai phân số 1/2 và 3/4."},{"prompt":"viết 1 đoạn code để tính tổng và thương 2 phân số 1/2 và 3/4 bằng ngôn ngữ C","completion":"Dưới đây là một đoạn code để tính tổng và thương của hai phân số 1/2 và 3/4 bằng ngôn ngữ C: \`\`\`c #include<stdio.h> // Định nghĩa cấu trúc phân số typedef struct { int numerator; // Tử số int denominator; // Mẫu số } Fraction; // Hàm tính tổng hai phân số Fraction add(Fraction a, Fraction b) { Fraction result; result.numerator = a.numerator * b.denominator + b.numerator * a.denominator; result.denominator = a.denominator * b.denominator; return result; } // Hàm tính thương hai phân số Fraction divide(Fraction a, Fraction b) { Fraction result; result.numerator = a.numerator * b.denominator; result.denominator = a.denominator * b.numerator; return result; } int main() { // Khởi tạo hai phân số Fraction fraction1 = {1, 2}; Fraction fraction2 = {3, 4}; // Tính tổng của hai phân số Fraction sum_fraction = add(fraction1, fraction2); printf(\\"Tổng của 1/2 và 3/4 là: %d/%dn\\", sum_fraction.numerator, sum_fraction.denominator); // Tính thương của hai phân số Fraction divide_fraction = divide(fraction1, fraction2); printf(\\"Thương của 1/2 và 3/4 là: %d/%dn\\", divide_fraction.numerator, divide_fraction.denominator); return 0; } \`\`\` Kết quả được in ra sẽ là: \`\`\` Tổng của 1/2 và 3/4 là: 10/8 Thương của 1/2 và 3/4 là: 4/6 \`\`\` Chúng ta đã thành công trong việc tính tổng và thương của hai phân số 1/2 và 3/4 bằng ngôn ngữ C."},{"prompt":"Summarize this: The year 1975 witnessed New Zealand welcome its 14th woman to parliament. A then 23-year-old Marilyn Waring found herself in a house of conservative white men, and instead of staying quiet out of gratitude for having a seat at the table, she spoke louder and more articulately than anybody ever had and perhaps has since. Marilyn pioneered feminist economics – a field that provides a well-needed gender lens to what some like to call “astrology for men”. Economics is a beautiful discipline with all its logic and charts. It is a school where everything seems to balance; supply meets demand and we have equilibrium. The field of economics has considered itself in such a state of equilibrium for so long that its theories have become core tenets of not just the discipline, but in turn all nation states. We put as much faith in economics as we do in the laws of gravity, the importance of procreation for the continuation of human existence, or the notion that causing harm to others is inherently bad. Economics is not, however, a science. Nor is it a philosophy or theology. It is politics with mathematics involved. Just as politics can be critiqued, influenced, and ultimately changed, so too can our understanding of economic theories. One does not need to be Adam Smith or John Maynard Keynes to challenge these core tenets; one can be an aspiring classical pianist who asks too many damn questions, i.e. Marilyn. Marilyn cut to the chase early on in her political career and questioned the measurement of gross domestic product (GDP), which by her first term was well and truly established as the key metric for assessing a country’s growth and progress. GDP measures all which passes through the market economy, so any good or service with a price tag that witnesses money changing hands. Marilyn’s GDP critique was ultimately two-fold: Firstly, GDP does not account for unpaid labour; a form of undervalued work that provides the foundations propping up the price-driven market economy. Marilyn drew back the curtain on worlds lost behind white linen on the washing line and showed the value these hidden people produce for our communities. She worked tirelessly to make the invisible women; the housewives; the mothers; the unskilled and subsistence labourers seen and counted. Secondly, GDP cannot decrease from transactions or events. As Marilyn puts it, GDP accounting has no debit side. Everything that passes through the market economy is counted as beneficial for growth. In a Canadian documentary made about Marilyn and her work, she used a great tale of an oil spillage and how the subsequent clean up, reparations to locals, donations to environmental groups, and so on, all involved an exchange of funds that collectively categorised the oil spillage as a complete success. Another example of this that Marilyn has often highlighted in her work is that war drives GDP. Notably, GDP was initially developed to assist in determining war financing. In fact, it was British economist Mr Keynes himself who wrote the paper “How to pay for the war” in 1940. By all accounts, war is amazing for GDP and the market economy. There are the investments in the latest warfare, the mobilisation and transportation of troops, the drain on the energy markets, the inevitable clean up and reparations… I mean you even have the unpaid and invisible people back home finally contributing by stepping up into the workforce. It is for these very reasons that an argument can be made that governments are incentivised, whether they are conscious of it or not, to engage in war and conflict. But how can anybody make the argument that war’s debits do not outweigh its credits, or even that war has no debits to begin with? Upon reflecting on the various monetary exchanges that would have occurred to achieve some of the twentieth century’s most devastating wars, I began to think of another war a lot closer to home. I asked myself, if those wars were so beneficial for GDP, then what does the war on women do for supposed growth? To begin we should define what is meant by the war on women. Its scope could be so wide and parameters bursting, and that is exactly how I intend to define it. The war on women is the million-year war, originating from the conception of patriarchal societies and spreading like syphilis across the globe. It begins and ends with simultaneously: 1) instilling fear in all women that threats of violence against their physical and emotional selves are always somewhat imminent, and 2) convincing men that they are entitled to be in control even if this means using violence. This fear in women and entitlement in men drives countless industries and revenue line items. Think of all the women who have sought crisis and therapeutic services in response to harm, the investments in hormonal contraceptives like they are a luxury item, or all the teenage girls buying razors at the mere sight of body hair because they have been told many times that boys get upset about that stuff, and they do not want to be unlovable, or worse still, make a boy upset. Think of the products that are moved off shelves in droves, because their advertisements, covertly or otherwise, allude to women’s subordination, and men as a result must have them. Think of the public spending on police forces, ambulances, courts and prisons, all in the name of safety. Think of the media industry and how it seems to win big each time another woman is found dead. Then think of the infrastructure attempting to curb this violence by putting in CCTV cameras and fluorescent lights, whilst most of the harm women experience is under dull bedside lamps in the comfort of their own homes. How many metaphorical band-aids have men and women bought to help heal the mental wounds of toxic masculinity and gender inequality? Could the act of Netflix binging to dull debilitating depression count as a metaphorical band-aid if the depression originates from feeling unable to be a real man? How many extra drinks have you purchased at the bar to reduce anxiety about how you look in your dress or if the drunk man is leering at you? Please, do not get me started on the cost of childcare. The war on women almost has no bounds; it permeates everything we know and hold true in society, just like the market economy. Instead of investigating the costs associated with the total subordination of women and how to use that knowledge to achieve gender equality, let us ponder a moment on the revenue generated by the war on women and what that can teach us. For perhaps then we can begin to unravel why we cannot seem to untie women’s oppression. Please note: opinions are my own and do not necessarily reflect those of my employer","completion":"In 1975, Marilyn Waring became the 14th woman to be elected to the New Zealand parliament. She spoke out against traditional economic theories and challenged the measurement of gross domestic product (GDP), arguing that it does not account for unpaid labor and that it cannot decrease from transactions or events. She also highlighted how war drives GDP and questioned the societal costs of the war on women. Waring argued that the war on women generates revenue for various industries and emphasizes the need to investigate the costs of women's subordination in order to achieve gender equality."},{"prompt":"[there would be dialogue in this story - alongside a title:] (It was just another day in the world of \\"Azur Lane\\". The commander was looking over the shipgirls of the Iron Blood. Just then, one of the Iron Blood's battleship shipgirls - Bismarck - started to feel...odd. Her left eye had come replaced with a red mass with a yellow eye - and the eye's pupil looked eerily similar to an octopus' pupil. She also had 8 red tentacles jutting out of her back - thankfully, they were noticeably short for now. But not even medical ships can find out had had happened to Bismarck. However, she seems to accept the strange red mass and tentacles as part of her.)","completion":"Title: \\"Twisted Loyalty\\" --- Commander: Bismarck, have you been feeling any discomfort lately? Your appearance seems... different. Bismarck: Ja, Commander. I cannot deny that something has changed within me. But fear not, I shall adapt and overcome. Commander: We cannot simply ignore this, Bismarck. We need to find out what happened and if it poses a threat to you or the fleet. Bismarck: Nein, Commander. I have accepted this alteration as a manifestation of my duty to protect the Iron Blood. As long as it does not hinder my capabilities, it matters not to me. Commander: But Bismarck, this is not a normal enhancement. Tentacles and an abnormal eye? We must investigate further. Bismarck: I appreciate your concern, Commander. However, my loyalty lies unwavering with the Iron Blood, no matter the cost. If this is the path I must walk to safeguard our fleet, then I shall embrace it. Commander: Bismarck, I understand your dedication to our cause, but we cannot turn a blind eye to an unknown power within you. We must consult with the research team and find answers. Bismarck: Very well, Commander. If it assures you, I shall cooperate. But know that my resolve remains steadfast. --- (Sometime later, in the research facility) Researcher: Commander, we have extensively examined Bismarck's condition, but we can find no explanation for this unique transformation. Commander: Is there nothing you can do to reverse or minimize its effects? Researcher: I'm afraid not, Commander. It appears that this change is not detrimental to Bismarck's combat abilities, and she is adjusting to the presence of the tentacles and altered eye. It is as if her body recognizes it as a natural part of her now. Commander: Bismarck, are you sure about this? Is there truly no discomfort or potential risk? Bismarck: I assure you, Commander, this transformation only serves to enhance my strength and solidify my devotion to our mission. The Iron Blood's victory will be assured. Commander: Very well, Bismarck. If you believe this alteration will only benefit our cause, I will respect your decision. Just remember, we are here to support you in any way we can. --- (Even with the uncertainty surrounding Bismarck's transformation, she continued to excel in battles, leading the Iron Blood to numerous victories. Her loyalty and determination never wavered, despite her unique appearance.) Commander: Bismarck, your courage and strength are remarkable. You have proven that even amidst change, loyalty remains unwavering. Bismarck: Danke, Commander. The Iron Blood's triumph is everything to me. I will continue to fight with unwavering devotion, no matter the challenges that lie ahead. (Commander and Bismarck stand side by side, ready to face whatever the unpredictable world of \\"Azur Lane\\" throws their way, united in their commitment to protect the fleet.)"},{"prompt":"Give me key points for a PowerPoint presentation slide for the following essay: • Skills – POINT 8  The strongest skills represented within the company/team of the small business history-based streaming service start-up could include: 1. Content creation: The ability to research and curate historical content, documentaries, and series. 2. Technical expertise: Knowledge of video streaming technology, platform development, and UX/UI design. 3. Marketing and promotion: Skills in digital marketing, social media, and content promotion to attract and engage Egyptian users. 4. Customer support: Providing efficient and 